<div>
    Attention all families:
FPS will provide bagged lunches for those who need it. If your family would like a bagged lunch, please call the school by 11:00. Today’s lunch will be pick-up only. Starting Tuesday, Wednesday and possible future days, town kids can pick up at school from 12:00-12:30. Lunches will be delivered to out of town students. Lunch will NOT be provided Thursday and Friday this week as it was scheduled days off.
When you call the school, please let the office know if you want lunch, if you will be pick up or delivery, and if you will continue lunches after this week if needed....</div>
